casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Sauter.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Sauter (1995), 73 Ohio St.3d 1209.]

(No. 95-1383 Submitted July 26, 1995 Decided July 27, 1995.)

The resignation as an attorney of Mark Stephen Sauter of Cincinnati, Ohio, Attorney Registration No. 0033014, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
